io.klerch.alexa.tellask.model

Class AlexaInput

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.klerch.alexa.tellask.model.AlexaInput

  • public class AlexaInput
extends Object
    This is the input for an intent request handing in all necessary information for handling the intent properly. Its counterpart is the AlexaOutput object.
